Every minute, hated it.

34
00:01:49,810 --> 00:01:51,277
Uh.

35
00:01:51,377 --> 00:01:53,614
17 miles,
is that what you said?

36
00:01:53,714 --> 00:01:56,517
16 and a half.

37
00:01:56,617 --> 00:01:59,620
♪ Pony boy carry me home ♪

38
