dad doing out here?

45
00:02:19,640 --> 00:02:22,308
Oh, he was probably heading up
to Tahoe or Vegas or somewhere.

46
00:02:22,408 --> 00:02:23,744
He liked to gamble?

47
00:02:23,844 --> 00:02:24,911
