in his address book.

59
00:03:09,389 --> 00:03:10,524
Barstow?

60
00:03:10,624 --> 00:03:12,859
He was in a motel.

61
00:03:12,959 --> 00:03:14,427
You weren't in touch?

62
00:03:14,528 --> 00:03:16,296
No. No, no.

63
