two nights ago doing 120.

71
00:03:40,954 --> 00:03:42,823
Hit a pickup truck.

72
00:03:42,923 --> 00:03:45,726
Killed himself, Miss Fox,
the driver of the pickup

73
00:03:45,826 --> 00:03:48,494
a, uh, Pedro Lopez,
father of six.

74
00:03:49,796 --> 00:03:52,766
'His blood alcohol
level was .33.'

75
00:03:52,866 --> 00:03:54,835
