79
00:05:05,839 --> 00:05:10,043
He used to think it was funny
to drive with his knees..

80
00:05:10,143 --> 00:05:14,414
...with his eyes closed,
like it was some sort of game.

81
00:05:14,515 --> 00:05:16,482
Idiot.

82
00:05:16,583 --> 00:05:17,818
Couldn't even
kill himself right.

83
00:05:17,918 --> 00:05:21,788
He has to...
take other people with him.

84
00:05:21,888 --> 00:05:24,658
Leave me
to clean up the mess.

85
00:05:24,758 --> 00:05:27,561
I don't think your dad planned
on dying out here, Doug.

86
00:05:27,661 --> 00:05:30,363
No, he never planned on doing
anything his entire life.

87
00:05:30,463 --> 00:05:33,366
He never planned to lose
our TV in a poker game.

88
00:05:33,466 --> 00:05:37,437
He never planned to be gone
for more than a couple of days.

89
00:05:37,538 --> 00:05:41,975
He never planned to...
hurt anybody in his whole life.

90
00:05:42,075 --> 00:05:45,111
Your dad lost
your television in a poker game?

91
00:05:47,147 --> 00:05:49,950
