of photos of you guys around.

123
00:07:18,505 --> 00:07:19,740
Yeah.

124
00:07:34,120 --> 00:07:35,155
You hungry? You want to get
something to eat?

125
00:07:35,255 --> 00:07:36,890
There's a taco stand
down the street.

126
00:07:36,990 --> 00:07:38,525
Ah, no, that's okay.
I'm not hungry.

127
00:07:38,625 --> 00:07:39,626
You go ahead
if you want to.

128
00:07:39,726 --> 00:07:41,528
I found this
in the closet.

129
00:07:41,628 --> 00:07:44,464
I think movies
or something.

130
00:07:44,565 --> 00:07:47,901
I didn't find much
to tell us about the wife.

131
00:07:48,001 --> 00:07:51,104
Just some clothes, cosmetics.

132
00:07:52,939 --> 00:07:54,474
No letters or
mail or anything.

133
00:07:54,575 --> 00:07:55,809
