211
00:13:39,119 --> 00:13:40,120
'Hey!'

212
00:13:41,387 --> 00:13:43,023
Hey.

213
00:13:43,123 --> 00:13:44,257
How you doing?

214
00:13:44,357 --> 00:13:46,259
You're a Broncos fan, huh?

215
00:13:46,359 --> 00:13:48,194
‐ Dallas.
‐ Dallas?

216
00:13:48,294 --> 00:13:50,564
I'm looking
for the Lopez family.

217
00:13:50,664 --> 00:13:52,332
Which one?
We got two of them.

218
00:13:52,432 --> 00:13:53,900
Uh, Pedro Lopez.

219
00:13:54,000 --> 00:13:55,135
He got killed
in a car accident.

220
00:13:55,235 --> 00:13:58,204
We're trying
to find his family.

221
00:13:58,304 --> 00:13:59,372
Not here.

222
00:13:59,472 --> 00:14:00,607
"Not here" like as in

223
00:14:00,707 --> 00:14:02,576
he doesn't live here
or "not here"

224
00:14:02,676 --> 00:14:05,245
like he's not here right now?

225
00:14:05,345 --> 00:14:06,513
Who are you?

226
00:14:09,282 --> 00:14:11,451
I'm Doug. Listen, can you,
will you do me a favor?

227
00:14:11,552 --> 00:14:14,420
