send some flowers.

255
00:15:32,065 --> 00:15:34,568
Doug, it's not your fault.

256
00:15:34,668 --> 00:15:37,103
It's tragic, but it
had nothing to do with you.

257
00:15:37,203 --> 00:15:38,939
You were thousands
of miles away.

258
00:15:39,039 --> 00:15:41,241
I know, it's just...
you know, I just..

